            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-Hd1e108">Rubrica 8</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De etate acceptabili discipline</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>
      ¶ De etate acceptabili disci
      <lb ed="#V" n="72" break="no"/>pline. Rubrica. 8. 
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="73"/> <ref>/ SAlomon in prouerbiis.
      <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>e. 22.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-Qd1e127">Adole
        <lb ed="#V" n="75" break="no"/>lescensliuxta viami suam etiam cum
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>senuerit non recedet. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-d1e135">
               <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>¶ <ref>Iesus filius sirach. in ecclesiast. c. 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-Qd1e139">A iu
        <lb ed="#V" n="78" break="no"/>uentute tua excipe doctrinam: et vsque ad ca
        <lb ed="#V" n="79" break="no"/>nos inuenies sapientiam.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-d1e148">
               <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>¶ <ref>Oratius inepistolis lib. i. c. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-Qd1e152">Nunc adhi
        <lb ed="#V" n="81" break="no"/>be puro Pectore verba puer: nunc te me
        <lb ed="#V" n="82" break="no"/>lioribus offer. Quo semel est imbuta recens
        <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>seruabit odorem Testa diu.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-d1e162">
               <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>¶ <ref>Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum. lib. 10.
        <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>c. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-Qd1e166">Quid stultius quam que diu non didiceris
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>non discere. Tandium discendum est quandiu
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>nescias. Si prouerbio credimus quandium vi
        <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>uas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-d1e178"> 
        / <ref>Idem de consolatione ad helbiam
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>matrem.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-Qd1e180">Altius precepta descendunt que
        <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>teneris imprimunt annis.</quote> <!--178.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="70-r"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-d1e194">
               <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>¶ <ref>Ualerius maximus. li. 4. ti. de studio et in
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>dustria:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-Qd1e198">Cato sextum et octogessimum an
        <lb ed="#V" n="3" break="no"/>num agens grecis litteris erudiri concupi
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>uit. Quam sero inde estimemus: quod etiam la
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>tinas pene iam senex didicit. Socratem
        <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>constat etate prouectum fidibus tractan
        <lb ed="#V" n="7" break="no"/>dis operam dare cepisse. Satius iudican
        <lb ed="#V" n="8" break="no"/>tem eius artis vsum sero quam numquam percipere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-d1e217">
               <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>¶ <ref>Lex digest. titu. de fideicommis. liber. l.
        <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>apud iulianum:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-Qd1e221">Iulianus dixisse fertur: etsi
        <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>alterum pedem in sepulchro haberem di
        <lb ed="#V" n="12" break="no"/>scere quid vellem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-d1e231">
               <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>¶ <ref>Uegecius de re militari. li. i. ti. 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-Qd1e235">Non tantum
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>celerius: sed perfectius imbuuntur que di
        <lb ed="#V" n="15" break="no"/>scuntur a pueris.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-d1e244">
               <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>¶ <ref>Cassiodorus epistolarum lib. 3. c. 11.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-Qd1e248">In
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>teneris annis acquiritur quod matura eta
        <lb ed="#V" n="18" break="no"/>te seruatur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-d1e256">
               <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>¶ <ref>Iacobus beneuentanus. c. 49.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-Qd1e260">Discere fac
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>artem puerili tempore natos: Tunc valet
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>ingenium discere cuncta bene: Nam postquam
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>mollis etas pertransit: ineptum Redditur
        <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>et durum quodlibet ingenium.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-d1e272">
               <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>¶ <ref>Prouerb. metricum. extraord. vel vag.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-Qd1e276">Quod noua testa capit inueterata sapit.
        <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>Qui non assuescit virtuti dum inuuenescitl
        <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>A viciis nescit discedere quando senescit.
        <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>Disce puer dum temptus habes dum sufficit etas
        <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>Tempora labuntur more fluentis aque.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-d1e290">
               <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>¶ <ref>Prouerb. vulga.</ref>  <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d57504-Qd1e294">A caual vcio no ense
        <lb ed="#V" n="31" break="no"/>gnare amblare.</quote>
            </p>
